            <lg xml:id="TK52">
<l>maṉaimāṭci yillāḷka ṇillāyiṉ vāḻkkai</l>
<l>yeṉaimāṭcit tāyiṉu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If domestic virtue be not in the lady of the house, life,</l>
<l>though it may have every virtue, is nothing.</l>
            </lg>
